/10/60minutes/main194051.shtml Mike Wallace interview on CBS with Farrakhan and Atallah Shabazz]\n* [https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-fix/wp/2015/10/11/louis-farrakhans-striking-two-hour-stemwinder-at-the-million-man-march-anniversary/ 2015 Speech at Million Man March in Washington DC]\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Farrakhan, Louis}}\n[[Category:Louis Farrakhan| ]]\n[[Category:1933 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:20th-century apocalypticists]]\n[[Category:20th-century Islamic religious leaders]]\n[[Category:21st-century apocalypticists]]\n[[Category:21st-century Islamic religious leaders]]\n[[Category:Activists for African-American civil rights]]\n[[Category:Activists from New York (state)]]\n[[Category:African and Black nationalists]]\n[[Category:African-American former Christians]]\n[[Category:African-American Muslims]]\n[[Category:African-American religious leaders]]\n[[Category:American conspiracy theorists]]\n[[Category:American former Protestants]]\n[[Category:American Muslim activists]]\n[[Category:American people of Jamaican descent]]\n[[Category:American people of Saint Kitts and Nevis descent]]\n[[Category:American social activists]]\n[[Category:American social commentators]]\n[[Category:Antisemitism in the United States]]\n[[Category:Anti-white racism in the United States]]\n[[Category:Anti-Zionism in the United States]]\n[[Category:Black supremacists]]\n[[Category:Converts to Islam from Protestantism]]\n[[Category:Discrimination against LGBT people in the United States]]\n[[Category:English High School of Boston alumni]]\n[[Category:Former Anglicans]]\n[[Category:Louis Farrakhan family| ]]\n[[Category:Nation of Islam religious leaders]]\n[[Category:Non-interventionism]]\n[[Category:People from Boston]]\n[[Category:People from the Bronx]]\n[[Category:People from Chicago]]\n[[Category:Religious leaders from Massachusetts]]\n[[Category:Religious leaders from New York City]]\n", "name_user": "Stafaa1978", "label": "safe", "comment": "Added link that gives a first hand account from a follower of Louis Farrakhan", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Louis_Farrakhan"}
